<paragraph blockId="15.[189,1399,1348,1409]" pageId="15" pageNumber="62">
The Feon’Ny Ala Hôtel (
<figureCitation box="[498,586,1348,1374]" captionStart="Fig" captionStartId="37.[189,232,1956,1982]" captionTargetBox="[241,1347,265,1917]" captionTargetId="figure-11@37.[241,1347,265,1917]" captionTargetPageId="37" captionText="Fig. 13. Damp forest at the Feon’Ny Ala Hôtel beside the Analamazaotra Special Reserve. Photo by courtesy of Dr Leonid Friedman (SMNHTAU)." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4983338" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/4983338/files/figure.png" pageId="15" pageNumber="62">Fig. 13</figureCitation>
